### US228 - Export route network in standard aviation formats

### Login como Backoffice Operator
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "backoffice",
  "password": "password"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
%}

---

### Exportar rede de rotas em formato GeoJSON
GET http://localhost:8080/api/routes/export/geojson
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/geo+json

---

### Exportar rede de rotas em formato KML
GET http://localhost:8080/api/routes/export/kml
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.google-earth.kml+xml

---

### Tentar exportar sem autenticação (deve retornar 401/403)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/routes/export/geojson

---

### Login como ATCC (não tem permissão para exportar)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "atcc",
  "password": "password"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("atcc_token", response.body.token);
%}

---

### Tentar exportar como ATCC (deve retornar 403)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/routes/export/geojson
Authorization: Bearer {{atcc_token}}
